                <note rend="inline" type="source">393.1123 Seymour, Walter F./15: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-07-17T19:00:00+08:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 17, 1928—7 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received July 17—11:42 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>545. Legation’s 377, May 21, 5 p.m. Following telegram has been sent to Shanghai:
                        <pb facs="0408" n="290" xml:id="pg_290"/>
                    <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“July 16, 3 p.m. Please deliver the following message to the Commissioner
                            of Foreign Affairs for transmission to the Minister of Foreign
                            Affairs:</p>
                        <p>‘Sir: With reference to my message of May 4 concerning the murder of Dr.
                            Seymour, and to that of your predecessor of May 19th, stating that
                            investigation had been ordered, I have the honor to request information
                            as to what has been done towards the apprehension and punishment of
                            those responsible for this crime.’”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">MacMurray</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
